            <p>Mysteries are full of suspense, and usually keep the reader guessing until the last moment.</p> 
            <%= link_to 'Add Cart',root_path,class:'btn btn-danger' %>
        </div>
         <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag 'book11.jpg',class:'cart-img' %>
            <h4 class="h4"><b>PLAYS</b></h4> 
            <p>Plays are written to be performed rather than read, but they’re still seen as a key literary genre. </p> 
            <%= link_to 'Add Cart',root_path,class:'btn btn-danger' %>
        </div>
         <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag 'horror.jpg' ,class:'cart-img'%>
