            <p>The genre has also spawned hundreds of popular horror movies.</p> 
            <%= link_to 'Add Cart',root_path,class:'btn btn-danger' %>
        </div>
         <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag 'book8.jpg' ,class:'cart-img'%>
            <h4 class="h4"><b>FANTASY</b></h4> 
            <p>Fantasy books are probably the most popular modern book genre. </p> 
            <%= link_to 'Add Cart',root_path,class:'btn btn-danger' %>
        </div>
         <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag 'book1.jpg',class:'cart-img' %>
            <h4 class="h4"><b>SCIENCE FICTION</b></h4> 
            <p>sci-fi books are usually bound by the laws of science as we know them in the real world.</p> 
            <%= link_to 'Add Cart',root_path,class:'btn btn-danger' %>
        </div>
         <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag 'book4.jpg' ,class:'cart-img'%>
            <h4 class="h4"><b>ROMANCE</b></h4> 
